I solved the issue...

In a different piece of code I had the following:

    private static final String GET_NOT_DISPERSED = &quot;select * from Assignments where &quot;
                                                + Assignments.CLOSE_DATE + &quot;&lt;=? and &quot; 
                                                + Assignments.PEER_START_DATE + &quot;&gt;=? and &quot;
